Reality TV star, Tacha and grandson of Afrobeat pioneer, Made Kuti have bagged massive endorsement deals with popular beer brand, Trophy. The duo was unveiled on the official handle Twitter handle of the beer brand as brand ambassadors for the Trophy ‘Extra Special’ stout. ‘Trophy’ welcomed the duo in two separate videos shared on their Twitter handle on Friday, March 18.   God’s love gifted me Austin Faani – Chacha Eke     2Baba and I renewed marital vows – Annie Idibia     I look better than most Nigerian girls – Bobrisky   Sharing a video advert of Tacha’s unveiling, the beer brand tweeted: “Welcome @Symply_Tacha to the Extra Special family, to create Extra Special Moments with us. “ For the Afrobeat singer, Fela’s grandson, the tweet accompanying the video read: “Let’s welcome Made Kuti to the Extra Special family as he introduces our Most Incredible CAN.”